text:
Need new clothes for the kiddos? For a limited time only, head in to Target where you can save up to 70% off select kids clothing items including the popular Cat & Jack brand! And did you know that Cat & Jack items have a one year warranty ?

Check out a few of the deals spotted… Cat & Jack Girls’ Tops only $2.10 (regularly $7) 
DPCI: 031-01-8839 
Cat & Jack Girls’ Denim Leggings only $2.10 (regularly $7) 
DPCI: 031-01-5987 

Marvel Avengers Wallet only $2.38 (regularly $7.99) 
DPCI: 202-09-1769 
Captain America Shirt only $2.68 (regularly $8.99) 
DPCI: 033-13-1771 

Cat & Jack Boys Hooded Sweatshirts only $4.49 (regularly $14.99) 
DPCI: 033-05-9130 
Cat & Jack Love Toddler Boys Long Sleeved T-Shirts only $2.97 (regularly $9.99) 
DPCI: 033-05-9136 
Cat & Jack Furry Vest only $4.78 (regularly $15.99) 
DPCI: 031-05-2167 
If you prefer to shop from home, it appears that some of these clearance items may be available at the same price online like select Girls Cat & Jack Tees priced at only $2.25 (regularly $4.50). Opt for free in-store pickup if available near you; otherwise, shipping is free on orders of $25 or more. OR – if you’re a Target REDcard holder , you’ll get FREE shipping on ANY size order and an additional 5% off your purchases!
